<title>Tuol Lenna Zion Tang</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gal in dawn un ngomei zam kal akhun,
 Tuol a lennau Zion tang ah;
 Suihlung guol in tuol a leng ui,
 Mu bang ngailo, lobang chul lei gam hi.

[V2]
 Ngilh ni umlo nau bang ka kap,
 Lalpa Na gam ngai in;
 Suihlung guol in tuol a leng ui,
 Lal nunnem chawian in.

[V3]
 2. Ei ngailo in gam nuom ah a leng ui,
 Nunghei lo ma tieng a sawn ui;
 Simlei hi nungsawn gam a hi,
 Pak lai sun ni a liem suihlung a hel.

[V4]
 3. A hun hung tung ding chu ka ngaklah ie,
 Nunnawp pielgal ei pui kai ding;
 Kikhen lo in lungtuok te tawh,
 Kumsawt pak tan in Lalpen chawian kau.

[V5]
 Sinsak sawmlenih te, Isu'n a sap haw chu-
 Peter Andrew Jakob, a suohpih Johan,
 Phillip Thomas Matthai, Jakob Alphai chapa,
 Thaddai Simon Juda leh Bartholomai.

[V6]
 Eile ei sam hi, eile ei sam hi;
 A sinsakte I hiu nang na hi keile;
 Eile ei sam hi, eile ei sam hi,
 A sinsakte I hiu, A na sem dingin.</lyrics>
</song>